{"tid":682216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《回帶》happy birthday to me! 岩布仙尼自己賀生辰","createTime":"2018-05-28T16:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T16:21:29.000Z","uid":162259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a317237f6baee8cf4b977cfd90c65eaf88ed53f9","tid":682216,"uid":162259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">岩布仙尼自己賀生辰</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2004年5月29日意大利甲組足球勁旅AC米蘭訪港，亞視邀請AC米蘭球員出席台慶節目。其中一名球員岩布仙尼的生日剛好與亞視台慶一樣，司儀朱慧珊便以廣東話邀請岩布仙尼唱生日歌，並以英文叫他開始唱。岩布仙尼一臉尷尬，唱出「Happy Birthday to me」。這個片段成為多年笑柄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/亞洲電視\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96&d=XtMOyMlXL4rulnteGpLBtfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=93b430ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/亞洲電視</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tL3qhZQJk7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtL3qhZQJk7E&d=XtMOyMlXL4rulnteGpLBtfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=bb937f4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tL3qhZQJk7E</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/002000_e77be648b581a9dd154ba3cbfccea527.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F002000_e77be648b581a9dd154ba3cbfccea527.png&h=920f9e7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恭祝所有5月29號生日嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME!</strong></span></span>"}]}